876
00:51:40,662 --> 00:51:43,780
Rym: And meanwhile, I realized that and bought a warehouse, which was key.

877
00:51:44,120 --> 00:51:52,200
Scott: Yeah, that was a crazy game because I felt like I was doing great in this one game of Puerto Rico, but then I forgot there was a fourth player and then my game fell apart.

878
00:51:54,203 --> 00:51:55,899
Scott: If it would have been a three player game, I would have won.

879
00:51:57,000 --> 00:52:05,980
